      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Foundation Level Extension –",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Agile Tester",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "That said, each extension level exam focuses on the learning objectives defined in that extension",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "syllabus. The relevant learning objectives at K1, K2, and K3 levels are provided at the beginning of each",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "chapter within each particular extension syllabus.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "2.4 Entry Requirements",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "To be able to participate in a Foundation Level Extension –",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Agile Tester exam, candidates must have",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "obtained the ISTQB Foundation Level certificate.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "2.5 Structure and Course Duration",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The Foundation Level Extension –",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Agile Tester syllabus has no shared or common elements with the",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Foundation Level syllabus.",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The syllabi must be taught in the following minimum number of days:",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Syllabus",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Days",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Baseline: Foundation",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Extension: Agile Tester",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "The following figure shows the structure of the Agile Tester Extension and its relationship to the",
      "page": 7
    },
    {
      "level": "H3",
      "text": "Foundation Level.",
